abstract="Smart Home has attracted significant attention from the research community in the recent years. Considerable progress has been made with the miniaturization of electronic devices for home automation and with the development of the technology of embedded system. The present work designs a smart and secure system based on various sensors and Raspberry Pi via the Internet of Things (IoT). This paper focuses on two aspects of smart home i.e. home security and home automation. This system is also designed to assist and support persons at home. It is intended to control appliances and the effective interactions to the persons. The user can visualise and control devices using internet, a webpage interface has been developed to help users to save the electrical energy by regular monitoring of home devices or the proper switching ON/OFF scheduling of them for more energy efficiency.",
