abstract="Rapid development in remote monitoring systems and communication devices have prompted the development of many services using Wireless Sensor Network in recent years. In hospital, patients' physiological parameter needs to be monitored continuously. The main objective of this system is to develop the wireless health care network for remote monitoring in real-time. This system also gives effective alternative to the wired devices used in the hospital for monitoring patients, which limits the patient to the bedside. The proposed monitoring system has an ability to monitor multiple patients' physiological parameters wirelessly. In case of any emergency, the system sends an alert message to the caretaker who help them to reduce the risk of patient life.",
