abstract="The healthcare industry suffers from a high degree of fragmentation which results in inefficiencies. It is widely recognized that the use of Information and Communication Technology (ICT) systems in health care has the potential to improve healthcare systems' efficiencies. The use of ICT in health care is referred as electronic health (eHealth). Four key steps are deemed essential for eHealth to improve healthcare delivery.",
