abstract="We are living in a technological era where many of the products are complex and have a large number of characteristics.1 For companies, it represents a big challenge to conceive the consumer requirements concerning the characteristics especially of technological products at a time when adapting to the customers' needs and wishes constitutes a main success factor for the survival of the company on the market. After all, the marketing process begins, continues, and ends through the decisions of consumers.",
