title="Trends in Individual Trajectories of Health Limitations: A Study based on the German Socio-Economic Panel for the Periods 1984 to 1987 and 1995 to 1998",
bookTitle="Ageing, Care Need and Quality of Life: The Perspective of Care Givers and People in Need of Care",
